BEAR'S PAW COUNTRY CLUB, INC., Appellant/petitioner(s),
v.
Tamara CANNON and Oliver Cannon, Appellee/respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D19-0048 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. February 11, 2019

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Petitioner's notice of withdrawal of petition for writ of certiorari is treated as a notice of voluntary dismissal of petition for writ of certiorari and is accepted. This proceeding is dismissed.
